        [ Both laughing ]

42:49.868 --> 42:51.668
Are you okay, Roland?

42:51.670 --> 42:54.971
             I mull da plat bee.

42:54.973 --> 42:57.774
       Senator?

42:57.776 --> 42:58.808
                  [ Groans ]

42:58.810 --> 43:00.009
    Are you okay?

43:00.011 --> 43:01.844
      [ Cellphone beeping ]

43:01.846 --> 43:03.346
   Roland?
                   [ grunts ]

43:03.348 --> 43:05.315
              Ah ca tah da foe.

43:05.317 --> 43:07.116
                  [ Laughs ]

43:07.118 --> 43:09.152
                 [ Groaning ]

43:12.157 --> 43:13.189
         No!

43:13.191 --> 43:14.757
     Just...stay.

43:14.759 --> 43:16.326
             All bee caa ta der.

43:16.328 --> 43:18.127
   Just stay here.

43:18.129 --> 43:20.229
  Stay here, Roland.

